quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,160,( aur qoum ) Loot ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhtlaya
  26,161,jab un se un ke bhai Loot ne kaha ke tum kyun nahi drtay ?
  26,162,mein to tumhara amanat daar paighambar hon
  26,163,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  26,164,aur mein tum se is ( kaam ) ka badla nahi mangta. mera badla ( khuday-e ) rab alameen ke zimmay hai
  26,165,kiya tum ahal aalam mein se larkoon par mael hotay ho
  26,166,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ne jo tumahray liye tumhari biwiyan peda ki hain un ko chore dete ho. haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum hadd se nikal jaane walay ho
  26,167,woh kehnay lagey ke Loot agar tum baz nah aao ge to shehar badar kardiye jao ge
  26,168,Loot ne kaha ke mein tumahray kaam ka sakht dushman hon
  26,169,ae mere perwar-digaar mujh ko aur mere ghar walon ko un ke kamon ( ke wabaal ) se nijaat day
  26,170,so hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko sab ko nijaat di
  26,171,magar aik budiya ke peechay reh gayi
  26,172,phir hum ne ouron ko halaak kardiya
  26,173,aur un parmeinhہ barsaya. so jomeinhہ un ( logon ) par ( barsa ) jo dry gay bura tha
  26,174,be shak is mein nishani hai. aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi they
  26,175,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai .
  26,176,aur ban ke rehne walon ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhtlaya
  26,177,jab un se Shoiab ne kaha ke tum drtay kyun nahi ?
  26,178,mein to tumhara amanat daar paighambar hon
  26,179,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  26,180,aur mein is kaam ka tum se kuch badla nahi mangta mera badla to khuday-e rab alameen ke zimmay hai
  26,181,( dekho ) pemana poora bhara karo aur nuqsaan nahkiya karo
  26,182,aur traazo seedhi rakh kar tola karo
  26,183,aur logon ko un ki cheezein kam nah diya karo aur malik mein fasaad nah karte phiro
